{"type": "article", "id": 29246, "title": "Prada 入驻最大时尚电商，以及，Elie Saab 高定系列不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-07T04:26:04Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 22, "name": "环保"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 2226, "name": "欧洲"}, {"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 2381, "name": "行李箱"}, {"id": 2721, "name": "回收"}, {"id": 3018, "name": "高级定制"}, {"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 16699, "name": "RIMOWA"}, {"id": 29892, "name": "Omega"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160707105056Iy2i1GBJ5HSxWltU.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/prada-to-launch-on-net-a-porter-mr-porter-10480922/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Prada 将入驻电商 Net-a-porter&nbsp;</b></a>｜7 月 15 日，奢侈品电商平台 Net-a-porter 将上线 Prada 早秋及秋季秀场精选单品，包括鞋包及皮具。当天奢侈品百货集团 Neiman Marcus 旗下的网站 mytheresa.com 也将发布 Prada 秋季成衣系列。男装奢侈品电商 Mr Porter 则将在 9 月 6 日推出 Prada 男装、运动装、鞋履及配饰。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Opening-Ceremony-opts-for-European-distributor,710975.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Opening Ceremony 选择欧洲经销商</b></a>｜纽约时装品牌 Opening Ceremony 为在欧洲扩张，选择与位于意大利摩德纳的经销商 Italian distributor Brama 合作，OC 的服装及鞋履将在 Italian distributor Brama  于欧洲、俄罗斯和中东市场的 showroom 展出。Italian distributor Brama 目前的合作伙伴包括 Equipment、J Brand、Grey Jason Wu 等。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-3675709/Aye-aye-Captain-Gigi-Hadid-keeps-string-hunky-sailors-line-takes-high-seas-nautical-Tommy-Hilfiger-ad.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gigi Hadid 为 Tommy Hilfiger 拍新香水广告</b></a>｜Gigi Hadid 近日为 Tommy Hilfiger 新推出的香水“The Girl”拍摄广告，2 月还为品牌在纽约时装周走秀。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Omega-enters-eyewear-market-with-Marcolin-Group-partnership,711095.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Omega 进军眼镜市场</b></a>｜瑞士钟表品牌 Omega 宣布与 Marcolin  集团达成合作协议，合作生产 Omega 品牌太阳镜。预计 2016 年 8 月上市，灵感来自 Omega 的品牌文化及腕表设计。Marcolin  的合作品牌包括 Tom Ford、Balenciaga、Moncler、Ermenegildo Zegna、Tod’s、 Montblanc 等。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Michael-Kors-unveils-new-fragrance-with-Lily-Aldridge,711244.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b> Michael Kors 与 Lily Aldridge  签约推出合作款香水</b></a>｜ Michael Kors  近日宣布与维密天使 Lily Aldridge  签约，推出一款香水“Wonderlust”，预计 8 月上市。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">Elie Saab 发布 2016 秋冬高级定制系列，还包括了亲子裙装：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104258kOSEtM4pGr9foD83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104300sQ08H52vXz4rykEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104306hWexqS6YlvUFEiV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104307gEIDNMA5vVXZzp8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104307WzKlSgdEcCeB2hoV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104310xpVmQHK8JbuLZPFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104310zRtSEy59vxFJkw0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707104313fB4nNXzQE8YocKyv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figu